{"tid":1969020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食環署︰食肆違令被檢控或不獲第二輪資助","createTime":"2020-04-12T06:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T07:24:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec365e117f8c0325ce7b8fc5fe82408ca856e6b4","tid":1969020,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:45:09.000Z","msg":"禁止多於4人聚集的「限聚令」（第599G章）3月29日生效，食物環境衛生署長劉利群今早（12日）在商台節目表示，署方至今巡查超過3.2萬次，發出超過1700次勸喻，亦有提出檢控；若食肆因不遵守規例被檢控，不排除不獲第二輪「防疫抗疫基金」資助。<br />\n<br />\n就首輪「防疫抗疫基金」，劉利群指出，政府支援飲食業界已批出逾2萬宗、涉及約27億元申請，預計最終會批出37至38億元。至於第二輪紓困措施，她說，適用於飲食業界的資助額一定不會少於38億元，希望老闆承諾不會裁員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200412/s00001/1586662261154/%e9%a3%9f%e7%92%b0%e7%bd%b2%e5%90%91%e9%81%95%e9%99%90%e8%81%9a%e4%bb%a4%e9%a3%9f%e8%82%86%e7%99%bc%e9%80%be1700%e6%ac%a1%e5%8b%b8%e5%96%bb-%e9%81%95%e4%bb%a4%e8%a2%ab%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7%e6%88%96%e4%b8%8d%e7%8d%b2%e7%ac%ac%e4%ba%8c%e8%bc%aa%e8%b3%87%e5%8a%a9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200412%2Fs00001%2F1586662261154%2F%25e9%25a3%259f%25e7%2592%25b0%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e5%2590%2591%25e9%2581%2595%25e9%2599%2590%25e8%2581%259a%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e9%25a3%259f%25e8%2582%2586%25e7%2599%25bc%25e9%2580%25be1700%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e5%258b%25b8%25e5%2596%25bb-%25e9%2581%2595%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%2588%2596%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%258d%25b2%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25ba%258c%25e8%25bc%25aa%25e8%25b3%2587%25e5%258a%25a9&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=adf20e35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200412%2Fs00001%2F1586662261154%2F%25e9%25a3%259f%25e7%2592%25b0%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e5%2590%2591%25e9%2581%2595%25e9%2599%2590%25e8%2581%259a%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e9%25a3%259f%25e8%2582%2586%25e7%2599%25bc%25e9%2580%25be1700%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e